<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="period-n">period <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'pɪəriəd/    美 /'pɪriəd/  </p>
<p>[C]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>(一段) 时间：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a period of 5 months 
5个月的时间</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Some fish can live out of water for a short <strong>period of time</strong>.
有些鱼能离开水存活一小段时间。</p><footer>2009 全国</footer></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>阶段；时期：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>children during the period of adolescence
青春期的孩子</p></div>

<h4 id="3-lesson">3.<strong>学时；课时 (lesson)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>What class do you have for first period? 
你第一节上什么课？</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a <strong>free / study period</strong> (= for private study)
自习课</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">派生词汇</h2>
<p>periodically /ˌpɪəri'ɒdɪkli/ adv   </p></div>